"ha imprigionato in questo corpo e non so come uscirne."

#: data/campaigns/Northern_Rebirth/scenarios/14a_Epilogue.cfg:547
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I believe Theta and I can help you with that, Abhai. Have no worries, you "
